text: The Mushak 200 is a long range Iranian missile. Zelzal-1/2/3 at missilethreat.com It has a range of 200 kilometers. Development of the Mushak series started in the year 1990 and the Mushak-200 was shown in 1998.Iran Missile Milestones: 1985-2020 iranwatch.org The rocket was based off the Zelzal 1 and parts of the Mushak's components were used in the Zelzal 3. The rocket has been given to Syria, Hezbollah, and Ansar Allah. == References == Category:Missiles Category:Rockets
